					"value": "PAD discussing the Colony, how eerie it is, and reflecting on the (similar) nautiloid at the beginning of the game.\r\n\r\nStarted through COL_Entrance_VB\r\n\r\nFor Wyll: discussing either his mission to save his father or Mizora.\r\n\r\n"
